	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Sattva</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Sattva#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Sattva#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Hindu philosophical concept</div>
<p><b>Sattva</b> (<a href="Sanskrit" title="Sanskrit">Sanskrit</a>: सत्त्व) is one of the three <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gu%E1%B9%87a" title="Guṇa">guṇas</a> or "modes of existence" (tendencies, qualities, attributes), a philosophical and psychological concept developed by the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samkhya" title="Samkhya">Samkhya</a> school of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hindu_philosophy" title="Hindu philosophy">Hindu philosophy</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-larsonp10_1-0" class="reference"><a href="Sattva#cite_note-larsonp10-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-jamesgsattva_2-0" class="reference"><a href="Sattva#cite_note-jamesgsattva-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The other two qualities are <i><a href="Rajas" title="Rajas">rajas</a></i> (passion and activity) and <i><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamas_(philosophy)" title="Tamas (philosophy)">tamas</a></i> (destruction, chaos). <i>Sattva</i> is the quality of goodness, positivity, truth, serenity, balance, peacefulness, and virtuousness that is drawn towards <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dharma" title="Dharma">Dharma</a> and <i><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jnana" title="Jnana">Jnana</a></i> (knowledge).<sup id="cite_ref-larsonp10_1-1" class="reference"><a href="Sattva#cite_note-larsonp10-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-ianwhicher124_3-0" class="reference"><a href="Sattva#cite_note-ianwhicher124-3">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc" role="navigation" aria-labelledby="mw-toc-heading"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2 id="mw-toc-heading">Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
