<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="Sattva#Buddhism"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Buddhism</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="Sattva#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
